@startuml
actor Admin
participant UI
participant ProductService
participant ProductRepository
database SQLite

Admin -> UI: กรอกข้อมูลสินค้าใหม่
UI -> ProductService: CreateProduct(code,name,price,qty,...)
ProductService -> ProductRepository: GetByCode(code)
ProductRepository -> SQLite: SELECT Product by code
SQLite --> ProductRepository: not found
ProductService -> ProductRepository: Add(product)
ProductRepository -> SQLite: INSERT INTO Products
SQLite --> ProductRepository: new ProductId
ProductRepository --> ProductService: ProductId
ProductService --> UI: Success
UI --> Admin: แจ้งเพิ่มสินค้าสำเร็จ
@enduml
